        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3843280310" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17264438210875995311">Why oh why had I not read The Curse of Chalion before now? It&apos;s such a wonderful book! So good I&apos;ll probably also buy a physical copy to enjoy.<br/><br/>It&apos;s a slow build, character driven political fantasy full of intrigue and heart. Much as I love my grim and gritty fantasy, sometimes a fantasy about a broken man trying to do good and make a better world is just what I need.</span>
  <span id="freeText17264438210875995311" style="display:none">Why oh why had I not read The Curse of Chalion before now? It's such a wonderful book! So good I'll probably also buy a physical copy to enjoy.<br /><br />It's a slow build, character driven political fantasy full of intrigue and heart. Much as I love my grim and gritty fantasy, sometimes a fantasy about a broken man trying to do good and make a better world is just what I need.</span>
